// Lifecycle of a single (possibly partial) refund against a booking's captured
// Stripe payment. A booking may have several BookingRefund rows (partial
// refunds), so the per-refund state lives here while Booking.stripePaymentStatus
// flips to REFUNDED only once the cumulative refunded amount reaches the total.
